<chapter xml:id="chapter_early_riphers">
	<title>Caesar's Shifty Idea </title>

<!-- Introduction -->

	<introduction>
		<p>
			In this chapter discuss ancient encryption systems:
			<ul>
				<li> Caesar's Shift</li>
				<li> Skytle</li>
				<li> Others?</li>
				<li> Slight improvements: Nomenclatures, Nulls, etc.</li>
			</ul>
		</p>
